g.text: make webapp responsive via Column Dropping -
Responsive Grid System - screen is divided in 12 equal parts.
offset - space to leave on the left side
m-1 margin of 1 unit on all sides
p-1 padding of 1unit on all sides
mx-2 margin of 2 units on left and right side
my-2 margin of 2 units on top and bottom
ms-3 margin of 3 units on left side
me-3 margin of 2 units on right side
mt-3 margin of 3 units on top side
mb-3 margin of 3 units on bottom side
